animeTitle: Renmei Kuugun Koukuu Mahou Ongakutai Luminous Witches
animeDescription: These are witches who defend everyone's smiles and fight enemies through the healing power of music. These witches, opposite of those in the defense fleet, are idols known as the Music Squadron.  (Source: MAL News)
